    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/e4b276b84fc558c37b2c3431be3725de.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/e4b276b84fc558c37b2c3431be3725de.webm?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>“我”已经当腻勇者？那就换“你”来当主角吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >延续《文字游戏》的经典机制“删、推、拆、组”进行探索与互动，用更多样化的主角，游玩更多元丰富的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/847fe902837a8ac9fc10d7f326b4d434.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/847fe902837a8ac9fc10d7f326b4d434.webm?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/847fe902837a8ac9fc10d7f326b4d434.mp4?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>我已经当腻“勇者”？那就换你来当“作者”吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以随心所欲创作剧情、布置谜题、设计关卡，打造独一无二的文字游戏。故事的走向、规则，全部都由你决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/dc9953d9b7d44d87a79f118324c5455f.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/dc9953d9b7d44d87a79f118324c5455f.webm?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/dc9953d9b7d44d87a79f118324c5455f.mp4?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/05535ba95ed7d34102c63c0d6d7b205b.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/05535ba95ed7d34102c63c0d6d7b205b.webm?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>官方主线「故事世界」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >延续《文字游戏》的主线故事，这一次，看见公主眼中的世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/ca827961d52442273da066bf253cbe76.webp?t=1771919361\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/ca827961d52442273da066bf253cbe76.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=658 /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>破格创意「平行世界」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更多无极限的文字玩法、各种跨界合作ＩＰ惨遭文字化</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/dad9a235d82dc38641253df0d2e993f8.webp?t=1771919361\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/dad9a235d82dc38641253df0d2e993f8.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" class=\"bb_img\" width=1170 height=658 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>还有⋯⋯</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/194aafb5735a3980c294c411933c1ac9.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/194aafb5735a3980c294c411933c1ac9.webm?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/babde9f49d249bf707601df25f8b169f.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/babde9f49d249bf707601df25f8b169f.webm?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/babde9f49d249bf707601df25f8b169f.mp4?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是自己闹着玩的恼人关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿来逗朋友玩的整人关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既能嗑又能玩的同人关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让网友跪着玩的神人关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ＯＯＯＯＯ玩的Ｏ人关卡</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以上，不需要会写代码，会用ＰＰＴ就做得到</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不必从零开始，所有现成关卡都能编辑与改写 </strong><br><strong> </strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/a7df9c55e6853e117b4d1ba78c16e025.poster.avif?t=1771919361\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/a7df9c55e6853e117b4d1ba78c16e025.webm?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114370/extras/a7df9c55e6853e117b4d1ba78c16e025.mp4?t=1771919361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>哇你很认真看到了最后耶！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为奖励，请查收宣传片中提及的100个文字梗笑话答案：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q1\t. \t有一只熊走过来，猜个成语\t｜A.\t有备而来（有Bear来）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q2\t. \tA到Z哪个字母最爱装酷\t｜A.\t西装裤（C装酷）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q3\t. \t麒麟飞到北极会变成什么\t｜A.\t冰淇淋（冰麒麟）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q4\t. \t熊剪了指甲会变成什么\t｜A.\t能</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q5\t. \t螃蟹为何横着走\t｜A.\t因为他有钱任性（有钳任性）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q6\t. \t什么动物每个礼拜二都会出现\t｜A.\t美洲鳄（每周二）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q7\t. \t大树跟小树差在哪里\t｜A.\t插在土里</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q8\t. \t皮卡丘左右横跳是什么\t｜A.\t皮卡乒乓乒乓</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q9\t. \t布和纸怕什么\t｜A.\t布怕一万，纸怕万一</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q10\t. \t哪一种神灵最好客\t｜A.\t欢迎光临（欢迎光临）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q11\t. \t举重选手比赛失利离开会场时会说什么\t｜A.\t珍重再见（真重再见）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q12\t. \t哪种职业最不容易受伤\t｜A.\t零售商（零受伤）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q13\t. \t蜜蜂停在月历上，猜个成语\t｜A.\t风和日丽（蜂和日历）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q14\t. \t不能在加油站打工的是什么人\t｜A.\t油腔滑调的人（油枪滑掉的人）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q15\t. \t哪位超级英雄最失败\t｜A.\t蜘蛛侠（Spider Man = 失败的人）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q16\t. \t李白是怎么死的\t｜A.\t失血过多（诗写过多）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q17\t. \t哪一种花单身最久\t｜A.\t牡丹花（母单花）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q18\t. \t一只老鹰叫Eagle，两只老鹰叫什么\t｜A.\t两GLE</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q19\t. \t美食掉到地上会变成什么？\t｜A.\t在地美食</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q20\t. \t为什么农夫爱喝全糖饮料\t｜A.\t因为他们种田（重甜）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q21\t. \t有一个字，人人见了都会念错。这是什么字\t｜A.\t错</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q22\t. \t你听过笑里藏刀的笑话吗\t｜A.\t哈哈哈哈刀哈哈哈哈哈哈</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q23\t. \t冰山能值多少钱\t｜A.\t一角钱（因为冰山一角）</p><p cla